he sent you to me.

41:20.200 --> 41:22.280
So, what he told me
is bollocks?

41:22.320 --> 41:24.520
No.
Of course not.

41:24.560 --> 41:26.640
You are her father, but you --
you haven't seen Anna

41:26.680 --> 41:28.280
in over eight years.

41:28.320 --> 41:30.240
That's because she wasn't
allowed to visit me in prison.

41:30.280 --> 41:32.480
The point is,
you haven't seen her.

41:32.520 --> 41:34.240
You know, they will argue
that your connection

41:34.280 --> 41:35.640
with Anna
has been broken.

41:35.680 --> 41:37.320
I wanted to see Anna.
I tried to see her.

41:37.360 --> 41:39.320
Regardless.
Secondly --

41:39.360 --> 41:41.240
"Is there a risk
that you having access to Anna

41:41.280 --> 41:42.640
will disrupt her life
to the extent

41:42.680 --> 41:45.280
