by that access?"

41:45.320 --> 41:47.600
Well, they'll have
a field day on that.

41:47.640 --> 41:49.440
You know, pointing out
that you were responsible

41:49.480 --> 41:52.360
for her mother's death,
that your extended family

41:52.400 --> 41:55.000
has a history of serious
criminal activity,

41:55.040 --> 41:56.880
and that you have been
arrested and questioned

41:56.920 --> 41:58.640
in a number of
murder investigations.

41:58.680 --> 41:59.920
I was never charged.

41:59.960 --> 42:01.880
Doesn't matter.

42:01.920 --> 42:03.480
They'll present it
as part of their case

42:03.520 --> 42:05.280
and argue that contact
with you

42:05.320 --> 42:08.120
will expose Anna
to a dangerous environment

42:08.160 --> 42:10.080
and reawaken
historical trauma.

42:10.120 --> 42:19.560
♪

42:19.600 --> 42:22.600
So, what you're saying is
I've no chance of seeing her?

42:22.640 --> 42:25.280
I'm saying it's not
going to be easy,

42:25.320 --> 42:28.120
and it's certainly not going
to happen any time soon.

42:28.160 --> 42:36.880
♪

42:36.920 --> 42:40.040
Jimmy:
You sure about this?

42:40.080 --> 42:43.000
'Cause I can do it
on my own.

42:43.040 --> 42:46.040
