44:06.520 --> 44:09.240
No, it doesn't
smell like him.

44:11.200 --> 44:13.720
No, it's --
it isn't him.

44:13.760 --> 44:16.360
It's not --
It's actually not him.

44:16.400 --> 44:18.160
No.

44:19.560 --> 44:22.560
J-Jamie doesn't
have a tattoo.

44:22.600 --> 44:26.160
No, I want to see Jamie.
That's not him.

44:27.480 --> 44:30.840
No, I just want to see Jamie.
Will you show me Jamie?

44:30.880 --> 44:33.120
Show me.
I want to see him now.

44:33.160 --> 44:35.600
I want to see him now.

44:35.640 --> 44:37.960
[Cries]

44:39.920 --> 44:41.840
[Breathes shakily]

44:41.880 --> 44:44.440
[Sobbing]

44:44.480 --> 44:50.400
♪

44:50.440 --> 44:56.000
♪

44:56.040 --> 44:58.240
Who's gonna pay
for this?

44:58.280 --> 45:02.240
♪

45:02.280 --> 45:05.160
You said whoever killed him
would pay.

45:07.440 --> 45:09.840
You promised me.

45:09.880 --> 45:13.880
♪

45:13.920 --> 45:16.880
Frank said that we
can't do anything.

45:16.920 --> 45:20.640
Fuck Frank.

45:20.680 --> 45:24.040
His son isn't dead.

45:24.080 --> 45:26.480
Ours is.

45:28.480 --> 45:30.840
That's not
Frank's doing.

45:30.880 --> 45:33.240
I don't care.

45:33.280 --> 45:37.600
♪

45:37.640 --> 45:41.040
It could be Anthony
next time.

45:41.080 --> 45:43.680
Have you
thought of that?

45:43.720 --> 45:47.680
I can't do something like this
on my own, Amanda.

45:49.760 --> 45:53.680
I need a driver,
at least.

45:53.720 --> 45:57.400
And no one's gonna help me,
not if Frank ruled against it.

45:57.440 --> 46:00.520
Ask Michael.

46:00.560 --> 46:03.560
He doesn't want to get involved
in any of this stuff.

46:03.600 --> 46:06.720
He's said that.

46:06.760 --> 46:08.840
Then ask him again.

46:11.080 --> 46:13.600
Tell him you need him.

46:16.160 --> 46:18.600
But I don't want to
have to do that.

46:18.640 --> 46:21.200
Just ask him.

46:21.240 --> 46:31.040
♪

