47:07.360 --> 47:15.040
♪

47:15.080 --> 47:17.000
You okay?

47:17.040 --> 47:21.080
♪

47:21.120 --> 47:25.600
I was Jamie's dad,
Michael, not you.

47:25.640 --> 47:27.280
Not you.

47:27.320 --> 47:28.760
I know you were.

47:28.800 --> 47:30.640
I raised him.

47:30.680 --> 47:33.040
I did everything for him.

47:33.080 --> 47:35.360
And he loved me.

47:35.400 --> 47:37.240
I mean, he said it all the time.
