48:05.640 --> 48:07.040
I know.

48:08.720 --> 48:11.040
If you were me,
what would you do?

48:12.680 --> 48:15.000
-I'd put it right.
-Yeah.

48:16.360 --> 48:20.000
'Cause if we don't, then what
the fuck am I, you know?

48:21.760 --> 48:24.080
If I can't do this for Jamie,
then what kind of father am I?

48:24.120 --> 48:26.280
I'm nothing.
I'm fucking shit.

48:26.320 --> 48:30.160
♪

48:30.200 --> 48:34.400
I can't do this alone.
I need help.

48:34.440 --> 48:37.160
And I wouldn't ask you if I
wasn't desperate, but I am.

48:37.200 --> 48:40.080
I'm desperate, Michael.
I need your help.

48:42.440 --> 48:44.560
Okay.

48:46.520 --> 48:48.800
Okay?
You'll help me get Moore?

48:50.720 --> 48:52.440
Yeah.

